name: Meadowbird Sonata
description:
I do what I do, so that the universal balance of which I am a part does not lose its balance.
Spontaneous creation is the reason there is something rather than nothing.
I like to create audio reactive geometries, and wait for the right moment to capture it in an image forever, until the "Big crunch" takes it all away.

Made in touchdesigner.
